This covers:
  - kyc-prover/   (ZK compliance prover)
  - pow-utils/    (proof-of-work / proof assembly helpers)
  - fb-schemas/   (FlatBuffer schemas)
  - ipfs/         (model-distribution helpers)
  - config/

The following subdirectories are third-party components under their own
